{
  "texts": [
    "First, there are not only different companies but also different states which might want to build AGI.",
    "Some of them, e.g.",
    "the US and China, are in an adversarial political relationship.",
    "Within these countries, we are currently in a situation where only a few selected companies have the ability to build systems at the level of the current cutting-edge.",
    "But this will probably change."
  ]
}